GeKoBridge - Class in lu.uni.geko.common
A utility class containing methods that are used by multiple GeKo plug-ins and that are GeKo specific (so they do not belong to an adapter class of lu.uni.geko.util.bridges).

(Note that it is disputable whether this class conforms to the bridge pattern as we are currently only providing one implementation and the "abstractions" can be regarded as low-level.)
